Serial numbers
Hardware vendor signatures
Electrical characteristics
Timing patterns


Trust Code Generation: Creation of cryptographic device certificates:

RSA/ECC key pair generation
Certificate signing with system root authority
Secure storage in hardware security module (HSM)
Backup and recovery mechanisms


Behavioral Baseline Creation: Establishment of normal device operation patterns:

Keystroke timing analysis
Mouse movement patterns
Command frequency profiles
Usage pattern modeling



Runtime Trust Enforcement:
When a device connects, M.I.T.E.L. performs:

